    Example data for linear model

    linear_data.Rd

    A simulated data set containing response variable, provider information and 10 covariates.

    data(linear_data)

    Format

    A list containing the following elements:

    data

    example data.time represents the observation time; status is the event indicator; Prov.ID is the center indicator (include 5 centers); Z1, ..., Z5 are 5 continuous covariates.

    Y.char

    variable name of the response variable.

    prov.char

    variable name of the provider indicator.

    Z.char

    variable names of covariates.

    Examples

    data(linear_data)
data <- linear_data$data
